    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812230/extras/033b90ecc92afdfe4730a9703663aaa3.avif?t=1739830025\" width=625 height=213 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Astro Chef, your ultimate cosmic culinary adventure!</h2><br>Become the galaxy's top chef in Astro Chef's chaotic kitchen! Ready to cook up a cosmic storm?<br><br>🚀 <strong>Culinary Adventure: </strong>Serve diverse dishes to alien patrons with unique preferences while navigating intergalactic kitchen challenges. Unleash creativity with alien ingredients and unique kitchen tools.<br><br>👫 <strong>Single Player &amp; Co-op:</strong> Restore your Uncle's restaurant alone or team up in co-op. One player uses the VR headset while the other handles the Kitchen Manual. Teamwork and communication are key.<br><br>👽 <strong>Extraterrestrial Cooking:</strong> Discover perfect combinations to delight alien customers. Create stunning dishes with unique tools. Fast-paced gameplay keeps you on your toes, ensuring meals are on time.<br><br>⚠️ <strong>Kitchen Chaos:</strong> Brace for chaos with space bugs, malfunctioning tools, and 'Out of Stock' challenges. Serve swarms of alien patrons and maintain the galaxy’s top lunch spot.<br><br>🎮 <strong>Challenging Progression: </strong>Advance through themed chapters with increasing dish complexity, testing your skills and adaptability. Each shift is randomized for a fresh experience. With each stellar rating, you're closer to becoming the ultimate Astro Chef.<br><br>🎨 <strong>Stunning Visuals:</strong> Enjoy vibrant art, detailed environments, and charming alien customers. Experience VR immersion with interactive feedback.<br><br>Ready to become the next Astro Chef? Join the cosmic kitchen chaos today!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812230/extras/ceb1fd9f9cb0f9f79721d12f852a2b1d.poster.avif?t=1739830025\" width=624 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812230/extras/ceb1fd9f9cb0f9f79721d12f852a2b1d.webm?t=1739830025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812230/extras/ceb1fd9f9cb0f9f79721d12f852a2b1d.mp4?t=1739830025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It's all about using wacky, out-of-this-world ingredients and tools to whip up the best dishes for your alien clientele. Who knew cooking in space could be this fun?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812230/extras/b5b1973d369f652ef9378241f4dea226.poster.avif?t=1739830025\" width=624 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812230/extras/b5b1973d369f652ef9378241f4dea226.webm?t=1739830025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812230/extras/b5b1973d369f652ef9378241f4dea226.mp4?t=1739830025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In Astro Chef, creating crazy dishes isn't enough. You'll also face wild scenarios like fixing broken tools with a hammer, dealing with EMPs, and more. Who said cooking should be boring?",
